-rights management.

*introduction: (IRM) This technologie allow to protect senseitive information from unauthorized access 

*Features : (IRM) typically have a number of features that allow an owner to control, manage and secure information from unwanted access.

*permissions management: It allow the users to protect their files against unauthorized users, IRM users can apply certain access permissions that permit or deny a user from taking certain actions and informations.
It also allows users to change or revoke access permissions without sharing the document again.
 
-change management  

=>|      Change management is moving your organisation/ project from own current states to own future states.
  |	 also change management means change in some details " Processes, systems, organization structure and job roles "		
 
  |      It means also sharing the documents with all the stakeholders, collaborate the work in the real time, make a branch for each individual work 
  |	 and finally merging the work for combining the best solution.  

if you want to make a change management, first thing you should folow these steps 
	
	first step in any change acknowleging and understanding the need for change, for example you see something needs fixing 

	second step you should comunicate with those who working with you to explored the situation and fully understand what needs to make. The communication with stakeholders framework gives you many idea to resolve the probleme or to ameliorate the system 
	
	third step if you really start thinking about change, it means that you have a great idea that makes your situation better than the older and many other solutions floating around you. A clear vision and a good idea can help you and help everyone who wants to amelioratefirst step in any change acknowleging and understanding the need for change, for example you see something needs fixing 
 

	4th  step if you really start thinking about change, it means that you have a great idea that makes your situation better than the older and many other solutions floating around you. A clear vision and a good idea can help you and help everyone who wants to ameliorate. So in this step you should determine all the values that are really need a change. develop a shot paragraph to explane what you see as a future of your project besides you should execute this vision with creating a strategy. 

	5th step you should recomunicate with your stakeholders to make the right decisions and slove all the probleme. this step allows you to remove all the obstacles and reach your goals. 
	
	6th step look for something that are not expensive that make you able to justify the investiment in each project 
after all that you should evaluate the progress, in this time if all going well you can celebrate success and if something wrong you can review your change and check you idea again with you stakeholders and fix the error if that possible.  

