About Onshape 

===> Onshape is an application focused on cloud. who offer a professional 3D computer aided design system that can help anyone on  design. This application allows the team to work together using any web browser or mobile application.

	Onshape helps the users to make a better design, also onshape has many features like  real time deployment, real time data management, real time change management, real time analyse and controls by using the cloud. 
	
	Onshape gives to the user the permission to share the document with someone who didn't have an account, in this time you can add what you want to work with you in the same document, you can choose what he can do 'edit, read or share' and also you can remove the access to the contact.
	
	Onshape is designed to be more reliable than standard software systems, such as those who didn't work in a parallel way.

	Us a result of cooperation you can find too many versions of work in many branches in your document, that helps you to choose the right branche to ameliorate your document.
	
	After choosing the right branche you can synchronize the work  
	
	If the project has many tasks and everyone has his own task, after finishing the work onshape allows the users to collect all the branches and make them in the same document 
	
	Many users working in the same document at the same time is referred to collaboration of the work. Any and all the features added or changed mmade displayed in real time to all the users in the project.
	
	User collaborating in the same document/project allows you to control what another user is doing in real time (FOLLOW MODE) 
	
	Real time data management is the information that is delivered immediately after collection. 

	Is created to solve the traditional management problems, which allows you to combines both functions. this step is one of the key benefits provided by onshape. 

	onshape have also an online version and offline version 
		the online version work on browser or mobile application 

		and the offline version it s against agile method, it makes you to work in your document but not in the real time. 
		
	Real time change management is the same meaning as change management in a general way, but this one has an extra meaning that it is executed in a short time. 
	
	 
